   Jialing River Basin (JRB). By analyzing spatial and temporal
   characteristics of SES and multiple typical ES, we investigate how ES is
   related to different SES types. The results reveal that: (1) from 1980
   to 2020, the SES of the JRB underwent significant transformations,
