   Arnold, Craig A. (Tom) and Fremier, Alexander K. and Garmestani, Ahjond
   S. and Craig, Robin Kundis and Gosnell, Hannah and Birge, Hannah E. and
   Allen, Craig R. and Benson, Melinda H. and Morrison, Ryan R. and Stone,
   Mark C. and Hamm, Joseph A. and Nemec, Kristine and Schlager, Edella and
   Llewellyn, Dagmar},
Title = {Regime shifts and panarchies in regional scale social-ecological water
