Funding-Text = {I had the opportunity and honor to work closely with David Pimentel for
   more than a decade in the late eighties and the nineties. Undoubtedly,
   David's intuition for environmental accounting, his enthusiasm for
   research and teaching, and his active engagement with emerging
   environmental concerns shaped my research career. Only now, after two
